[32m│[0m ### **Critical Vulnerability Details**                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Type**: CWE-347 - Improper Verification of Cryptographic     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Signature                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Issue**: The application accepts JWT tokens with `"alg":"none"` algorithm, [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m which means NO signature verification is performed. This allows attackers    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m to:                                                                          [32m│[0m
