[32m│[0m - Modify token claims (e.g., change role from "user" to "admin")             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Bypass authentication without knowing signing keys                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Escalate privileges without any cryptographic validation                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ---                                                                          [32m│[0m
